Class DrillClientTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.test.BaseTest
      • org.apache.drill.test.DrillTest
        • org.apache.drill.exec.ExecTest

            • org.apache.drill.exec.DrillSystemTestBase
              • org.apache.drill.exec.client.DrillClientTest

  • public class DrillClientTest
extends DrillSystemTestBase
    The unit test case will read a physical plan in json format. The physical plan contains a "trace" operator, which will produce a dump file. The dump file will be input into DumpCat to test query mode and batch mode.
